hopobject.body: Special Delivery buy nexium australia Boreman was recuperating in Florida from a serious car accident in 1969 when she first attracted Traynor's attention, and her story of abuse began before they were even married. The gang rape that seemed to end Lovelace's marriage in the new film was actually what kicked off Traynor's abusive extremes in their relationship. Her body was his currency — as a source of income and a means of payment; he even allegedly pimped her out to a doctor to pay for the silicone breast injections he wanted her to have. Prostitution then paved the way for 8-millimeter smut films, as Traynor forced her into increasingly taboo scenarios that culminated with her infamous short, "Dogarama."
